Go get what YOU want. 
Don’t hold back!!

Life is too damn short to sit back and let your biggest dreams just fade and disappear. They matter. And YOU matter.

When you do that certain “ something” that makes you feel the most alive and high on life. 

Do it. 👌🏻✨
Don’t settle.

You can do anything. 
And I legit mean it. 

Just don’t give up, be kind to yourself, take it day by day, live your life with a positive mindset and appreciate every day you wake, and every breathe you take. 
And then your life will make more sense again. 👌🏻❤️

You deserve the best. 
So go get ‘em Tiger!!
Go live your dreams and don’t hold back!!🖤💋😘✨

remember…💗

Y’all when I heard this, it’s spoke to me on so many levels. 
As an artist, as a full time dreamer, this, so hit me like a ton of bricks. 🙈

Every day that I get to do what I love I soak it in like crazy!!☺️🦋🎬

I’m so so grateful to be where I am in life. 🙏🏻 

Not just because I booked a job, but just to still be here, rocking and rolling and not giving up. 🤙🏼🌸

This world is so beautiful and this world can be so cruel. It depends on how you want to view it. 

It depends on how you want to live your life. 

I suggest, despite all of the icky stuff you choose what makes your heart and soul radiate. ✨❇️✨

Do something that matters to you. 💗

Be proud of yourself. 💗✨

Each and everyone of you have come leaps and bounds. 💗

Celebrate your life! 🎉 
Give your self, so much love 💗 and enjoy this beautiful life🌸💕

I won’t change by the glamorous 💕💋

Ever since I was a little girl, I always loved this song even before I really knew what it meant. 😂
So funny, I’m still that young girl, who feels so confident and free! 
I mean I have my days like everyone else 😜but when I’m feeling myself, I’m feeling GOOOOD.
And I will say as much as my inner child can get me in trouble🙈
Sometimes I have to remember to love it. 💕
We all still have our inner child in us. 
Forever.
We all have our own unique, vibrant, and lovely self-expressions that when we begin to grow older we tend to feel like we have to hide it.
Well I say, Let’s love it more. 💕💕
That’s what I’m learning. 
But to remember your higher self is in the driver seat but yet you love your inner child in the car seat. You don’t ignore it, you listen, embrace, let go & love.

Annd on another note..

Now being an adult, I will say my inner child was spot on with this song. 🤘🏻
I absolutely love the message Fergie displays about no matter what success , whatever cool experiences she gets, she still down to earth and still is grounded. 🤙🏼💕
She still drive through Taco Bell raw as hell 🔥🤘🏻

We’re all the same. 

Okay ✌🏻 love y’all 💕

I continue to work on my healing journey EVERY single day.🤙🏼

I value and honor my own time. 

Before I used to feel Guilty for dedicating so much time for ME.
But then I woke up and realized 

“ Who cares?! At the end of the day I am still me. And if I am not filling my own cup, how the heck am I able to help fill others”

And I was noticing I was getting worn out and drained easily. Felt like 💩 all the time, & becoming  more irritable & depressed 🙈

And I then realized, 
I don’t wanna live like that anymore. I can’t. 
And
I don’t have to.

I want to live this life in a 
calm, kind, peaceful, and healthy way.

 And I knew I wasn’t living a healthy lifestyle. 
I was ignoring myself. I kept saying I was “good” and continued to let myself go. 
Even when no one knew because  I have always been good at masking it.

But y’all…
I’m done doing that!! And I encourage all of you to do the same. 💜

Please

Be selfish. 
Be honest.
&
Choose you. 
❤️
At the end of the day you’re only going to have yourself forever.

No matter all the people you meet in this beautiful world,
You will always have yourself. 

So please take care of yourself.  Honor yourself
&
Love yourself hella.

&
Have a self-love filled day 💗💗

It’s really 
truly 
amazing when you decide to take a step back from a hidden toxic energy 
and
 a bad environment 
and realize… how beyond better you are without it! 

These last couple months I have had so many answers come to light. 

And to be completely honest some/ most of the answers I received, were heartbreaking, cruel and hurtful. 

I didn’t want to believe that I was willingly in an unhealthy, mentally abusive and dangerous environment. 
But after all of this time, space and healing I feel like I am on finally on the other side!!!😍😊❤️

Instead of always feeling confused, drained, insecure, tired, depressed, & anxious. ( how I felt before my realizations) 

Now I feel RENEWED, CLEANSED, REFRESHED, and HEALED.🦋

Of course, as humans we will have feelings that don’t always feel great. 
But that’s called having feelings. 
And being human. 
And I wouldn’t want to have it any other way!! 

But once you find the awareness of how you can actually live a healthy, kind, true and honest life it really does seem to make life much 
easier and calmer. 

I know I am not the only one and that I am not alone.🤙🏼❤️

I am so beyond grateful for all of the beautiful souls in my life. 
Especially those who have had my back and have supported me through this emotional journey.🦋

And I would like to shout out my amazing boyfriend @bruceclifford_ ❤️

He has been such a rock to me. Like holy hell he has!!!He has seen me go from my highest to my absolute lowest. ( which was pretty low)…
And yet still he makes me feel so safe, secure and loved. ❤️

Please take care of yourselves, protect your energy and follow your intuition. It NEVER lies.

Have a beautiful and kind day 💗

Xoxo,
Kirsten Ann🦋

You can feel the closest with someone and within a couple days/ months/ years etc they turn into strangers due to changes in this thing called life.

I personally can’t eject my love for someone out of my heart I just am not built that way. I will always have love for them as I felt it and I will never deny what I felt.

I am a lover. I am a soul who chooses to “ connect, listen and love”.

So if you see this, please know YOU are LOVED. 💜

Let’s not live so “ isolated” let’s “ come together”
WE ALL ARE CONNECTED. 🤙🏼

I send my love to you all! ♥️

Go have a GREAT day!!

Love you!!!
